Logical Fallacy

Logical Fallacy are the chunks that Data Scientist need to over come and be aware and beware of.

Cognitive biases are tendencies to think in certain ways that can lead to systematic deviations from a standard of rationality or good judgment, and are often studied inpsychology and behavioral economics.

(https://welcomedata.wordpress.com/2015/01/25/cognitive-biases-logical-fallacies-impact-on-public-policy/)

